      • NotationStack

      • NotationStack

        public NotationStack(int initialCapacity)
        This constructor accepts an integer argument as a parameter to initialize the size of the stack. The topIndex field is set to -1 so that the first entry pushed to the stack has index 0.
        Parameters:
        initialCapacity - The initial capacity of the stack array.
